Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:12.04,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}却渐渐辨不清形状
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:17.84,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}若要将恨意驱赶出心房
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:23.43,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}还如何让你把命偿?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:29.31,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}掘尘封过往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:35.44,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}只为填罪业汪洋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.65,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}怨凛冽锋芒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:47.33,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}颔首抚刻骨心伤
